title: Sample Book, Laverne Marbalia, 1957
description:
Collection of marbled papers in many different colors and styles. First page is a price list of patterns dated June 1957.

102 pages of samples.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, Laverne Marbalia, 1957; Manufactured by Laverne International, Ltd. (United States); USA; hand painted paper; H x W: 16.5 x 21.5cm (6 1/2 x 8 7/16in.); Gift of Laverne International; 1969-55-1-1/102
